1
00:00:36,359 --> 00:00:37,039
Minjiang

2
00:00:37,399 --> 00:00:38,280
What are you talking about?

3
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:39,479
Which one is your master?

4
00:00:39,799 --> 00:00:40,880
Go pour tea for Director Zhen, hurry.

5
00:00:42,679 --> 00:00:43,479
Manager Liu

6
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:46,000
Your factory is quite something.

7
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:47,960
Not only do you make my student...

8
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:50,240
...a dignified Grade-8 Worker carry cement...

9
00:00:50,679 --> 00:00:53,119
...but also do the work of serving tea and water.

10
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,280
Zheng Minjiang...

11
00:00:57,439 --> 00:00:58,600
...is your student?

12
00:00:59,320 --> 00:00:59,520
This...

13
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,280
Minjiang...

14
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,920
...is the student I value most.

15
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:05,599
You rascal.

16
00:01:06,239 --> 00:01:07,480
You haven't come to see me for so long.

17
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:09,959
Have you forgotten your master?

18
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,040
You are my mentor.

19
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:12,400
How could I forget?

20
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,480
I haven't accomplished much all these years.

21
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,439
I was afraid of shaming my master.

22
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,280
That's why I was too ashamed to see you.

23
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,159
I made many calls before.

24
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:24,480
I wanted to transfer you to the province.

25
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,400
What were you thinking?

26
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,280
You contacted the factory before?

27
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:30,359
You didn't know?

28
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,319
Director Wu.

29
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,439
What is going on here?

30
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:39,879
D-Director Zhen...

31
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,560
I...

32
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,640
It was an oversight.

33
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,359
I cherish talent.

34
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,439
Minjiang...

35
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,040
...is too...

36
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,599
...t-t-too outstanding. I...

37
00:01:45,599 --> 00:01:47,120
You're talking nonsense.

38
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,319
I see your little schemes...

39
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,799
...are written all over your face.

40
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:51,319
I...

41
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,239
Minjiang.

42
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,680
I did you wrong.

43
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,359
Please speak to Director Zhen for me.

44
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,879
You can't even pass a message...

45
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,719
...yet you dare to frame Minjiang?

46
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:09,919
About doing private work?

47
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,159
I think your head...

48
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:14,159
...isn't fit to be a Director anymore.

49
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,360
Minjiang.

50
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,560
I know I was wrong.

51
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,680
Please put in a good word for me.

52
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:28,000
Master.

53
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:29,960
It wasn't easy for you to come here.

54
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,560
There's no need to get angry over this.

55
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,240
Exactly, exactly.

56
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:34,960
Right.

57
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,520
Zhen Zhen.

58
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:36,960
Come.

59
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,520
Say hello.

60
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:38,919
Brother Minjiang.

61
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,080
Do you remember me?

62
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,479
Zhen Zhen.

63
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:43,759
Long time no see.

64
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,159
Dad and I came back this time...

65
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,120
...just to visit your factory.

66
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,199
That's easy.

67
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,280
I'll show you around.

68
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,280
Good.

69
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,120
I also want to see...

70
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,960
...if the things your master taught you...

71
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,680
...have all been forgotten.

72
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:56,759
Master Zhen.

73
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,039
This way.

74
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,280
Minjiang.

75
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,879
How have you been at the factory these years?

76
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,000
It's alright.

77
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,919
You useless lot.

78
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,840
Look at the stupid things you've done.

79
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:16,800
Xiaochuan

80
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,520
Go buy some Tianfu Cola.

81
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,240
And...

82
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,039
buy some spicy chicken too.

83
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,520
And that...

84
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,919
braised pork knuckle.

85
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,240
Boiled sliced beef.

86
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:29,520
Get it from Xiaofang's place.

87
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,879
We have a distinguished guest today.

88
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,280
It's an honor to have you here.

89
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:34,520
We can't be negligent.

90
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,479
Alright, Mom.

91
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,439
Our family...

92
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,439
has money now.

93
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,560
We can afford it.

94
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,280
Chuan.

95
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,199
Hurry up, go.

96
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,159
What a show-off.

97
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:50,280
Director Zhen.

98
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:52,680
Please enjoy the food and drink.

99
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,520
Make yourself at home.

100
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:56,159
I just came to visit my student's home.

101
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:56,960
Mother Zheng,

102
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:58,639
you're too kind.

103
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,120
You're making it so that next time,

104
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,680
I won't dare to visit.

105
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:02,560
Director Zhen,

106
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,439
you must come often.

107
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:07,960
Our Minjiang is still waiting for your guidance.

108
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,520
I took a tour of the factory today.

109
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,159
I could see that

110
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,639
Minjiang

111
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,639
is steady and reliable in his work.

112
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:17,079
I'm very satisfied.

113
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:20,680
Master,

114
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,639
I'm still just an ordinary worker.

115
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,879
I've disappointed you.

116
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,079
I know about your technical skills.

117
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,680
You have absolutely no issues there.

118
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:28,959
Here, Mother Zheng.

119
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:30,759
Come, Director Zhen.

120
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:35,879
That's right.

121
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,079
His skills...

122
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,759
are excellent.

123
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:39,079
He takes after his father in that regard.

124
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,319
You wouldn't believe it,

125
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,639
a while ago,

126
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,639
he went to that Sino-Hong Kong joint venture factory

127
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,639
to fix their machines.

128
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,680
He even earned 10,000 yuan.

129
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,879
Mom.

130
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,480
Minjiang's abilities...

131
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:52,839
as his master, I know them best.

132
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,199
I came here this time

133
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:58,120
specifically for you.

134
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,839
For me?

135
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:03,079
Your factory is currently restructuring.

136
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,639
The restructuring of state-owned factories isn't easy.

137
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,680
This task has fallen to me.

138
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:11,000
Regarding your factory,

139
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,680
our working group has conducted a survey.

140
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,920
The conclusion is

141
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,959
the factory leadership needs to change.

142
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,040
Especially the factory director.

143
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:20,560
I came here

144
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,720
to decide on the new factory director.

145
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,000
Would you

146
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,920
be willing to give it a try?

147
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:31,120
Me?

148
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,279
Of course.

149
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,480
You...

150
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,160
don't have much management experience.

151
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:37,879
At first, we'll assign a few

152
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:39,519
experienced people to assist you.

153
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,439
I know.

154
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,360
The factory isn't doing well right now.

155
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:47,040
With the current group of people,

156
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,720
if they continue leading like this,

157
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,199
this factory will...

158
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,959
I'll do it.

159
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:58,959
But I also know

160
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:03,240
that President Tang's Sino-Hong Kong joint venture factory

161
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,319
offered you very high compensation

162
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:07,480
to be a Technical Consultant.

163
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,279
If

164
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,680
you choose to stay at the state-owned factory

165
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,439
and shoulder the heavy burden of restructuring,

166
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,480
the compensation

167
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:16,959
definitely won't compare,

168
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:20,199
and the load won't be easy to carry.

169
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,879
Have you

170
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,680
really thought this through?

171
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,240
I have.

172
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:31,519
Starting from my mom and dad's generation,

173
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,279
they've worked in the cement factory.

174
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:34,959
I took over their position too,

175
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,040
and I'm very familiar with it.

176
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,319
Restructuring isn't a burden,

177
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:41,040
but a way to give the old factory new life.

178
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:44,240
I hope our factory can regain its former glory.

179
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,160
By optimizing the production structure

180
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:47,519
and expanding market channels,

181
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,759
we can give key technicians a stage,

182
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,439
and provide security for frontline workers.

183
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,600
The factory spirit of making quality goods for the country

184
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:54,759
will be passed down through generations.

185
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,519
Good, Minjiang.

186
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,879
As your mentor,

187
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:00,959
I really didn't misjudge you.

188
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,120
Thank you, Master, for the opportunity.

189
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,120
Zhenzhen, don't stand on ceremony.

190
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:08,720
Eat up.

191
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:14,439
Zhenzhen, during this time,

192
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:17,279
is transferring to the Chunjian Vinegar Factory in your city.

193
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:20,360
You'll have to look out for her from now on.

194
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:22,920
Brother Minjiang,

195
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,160
sorry to trouble you in the future.

196
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,639
It's no trouble at all.

197
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:29,720
Come, eat.

198
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,439
Thanks, Mom.

199
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,480
Master, please have some food.

200
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:32,079
Okay.

201
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:35,519
Master, wait a moment.

202
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,279
I'll go call a car over.

203
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,480
Wang Yingrong.

204
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,079
What do you want?

205
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,240
You...

206
00:07:45,439 --> 00:07:46,560
have you eaten yet?

207
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,160
None of your damn business.

208
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,040
I did say I liked you before,

209
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,720
but I haven't done anything to you.

210
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,079
If I, a girl, am not making a fuss,

211
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:02,120
why are you, a grown man,

212
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,480
acting so awkward here?

213
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,639
Actually, I regret it.

214
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:08,759
I actually...

215
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:09,279
Director Zhen,

216
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,639
apologies for the humble hospitality today.

217
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,079
Please come often in the future.

218
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:13,160
Okay, okay, I will.

219
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,920
And you too, Zhenzhen.

220
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,839
Since you've transferred here,

221
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,680
from now on,

222
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,360
you'll see Minjiang every day.

223
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,759
Don't be a stranger.

224
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:26,079
Come to our house for meals.

225
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:28,040
If Minjiang dares to neglect you,

226
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,959
just tell me.

227
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:30,079
I

228
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:31,560
won't let that brat off the hook.

229
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,279
This is my mentor's daughter.

230
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,639
She just transferred to the vinegar factory.

231
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,080
She came for official business today.

232
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,480
Why are you telling me this?

233
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:44,799
I...

234
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:45,879
Minjiang!

235
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,080
Minjiang!

236
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:49,279
Minjiang's Mom,

237
00:08:49,799 --> 00:08:51,039
we're heading back now.

238
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:52,360
Let's go.

239
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:55,639
Master,

240
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,799
take care on your way back.

241
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,960
Take care.

242
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:12,080
Still thinking about it?

243
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,559
That neighbor girl of Minjiang's.

244
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:17,679
Back when Brother Minjiang

245
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:19,360
went to the provincial Light Industry Bureau training center

246
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,480
for his advanced studies,

247
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:22,559
he mentioned this neighbor to me.

248
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,039
I know who she is.

249
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:25,759
Her name is

250
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,039
Wang Yingrong.

251
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,919
Minjiang told you a long time ago

252
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,759
that he likes this girl.

253
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,279
Dad.

254
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,559
How did you know?

255
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,759
Your feelings for Minjiang,

256
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:43,960
aren't hard for Dad to see either.

257
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,960
Minjiang is someone

258
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,080
I admire very much.

259
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:50,679
Dad supports you

260
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:54,120
in bravely pursuing your own love.

261
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:56,159
But I must also remind you,

262
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,600
matters of the heart

263
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:58,919
cannot be forced.

264
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:00,559
And there is no right or wrong.

265
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,840
I understand, Dad.

266
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:18,080
Take a break.

267
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,120
Sister Yingrong.

268
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,200
Haven't you noticed

269
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,840
that screw press in our factory

270
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,759
works really well?

271
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:31,879
Do you know why?

272
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,840
It's because my big brother improved it.

273
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,120
When did he come here?

274
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,759
Tell him not to mess with things.

275
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:42,360
He can't afford to pay if he breaks it.

276
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,919
Machines are certainly important,

277
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,360
but grain to wine, wine to vinegar,

278
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:46,720
manual fermentation,

279
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:47,519
and sun exposure...

280
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,960
every step requires care.

281
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,440
Otherwise, you can't brew good vinegar.

282
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:53,279
What you said is definitely important,

283
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,480
but machines are important too.

284
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,360
All those containers and pipes,

285
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:58,120
were all fixed up by my big brother.

286
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,000
They definitely work well.

287
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:00,120
Well...

288
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:02,799
What are you doing?

289
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,440
I didn't lie.

290
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,440
Yingrong.

291
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:06,320
Yingrong!

292
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,080
Sister!

293
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:07,600
Yingrong!

294
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,519
What's wrong?

295
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,320
Bao'er...

296
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:12,279
Li Guangming's mom took Bao'er away.

297
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:14,519
What?

298
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:16,960
Let's go find them.

299
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,279
Let's go.

300
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:28,559
My son owes so much money.

301
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,440
I'll sell this money-loser to pay it back.

302
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,879
Sis, don't worry yet.

303
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:37,759
She is Bao'er's grandma.

304
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,519
She won't do anything to her.

305
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,840
She doesn't like Bao'er.

306
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:40,799
She really doesn't.

307
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:41,759
How could she?

308
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,879
She... she...

309
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,039
Maybe...

310
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,399
she just hasn't seen Bao'er in a while.

311
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:46,200
And missed her.

312
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:46,639
Right.

313
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,480
Maybe...

314
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,679
she's at the Li house right now.

315
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:50,240
Sis.

316
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,039
Wait for me.

317
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,200
I'll take you there.

318
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:54,360
Yingrong.

319
00:11:56,279 --> 00:11:56,759
Zheng Minjiang.

320
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,279
Lend me your car for a second.

321
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,159
What's wrong?

322
00:11:59,639 --> 00:12:00,039
Bao'er.

323
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,639
Bao'er was taken away by the Li family grandma.

324
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:03,159
I need to find Li Guangming and his mother.

325
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,120
Get in, I'll take you.

326
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:04,720
Wait a minute.

327
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,279
Are you sure the kid is at the Li house?

328
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:08,159
I...

329
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,600
I... I don't know.

330
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:12,840
Haiyang makes a point.

331
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,279
We have to split up.

332
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:16,759
An old lady carrying a child can't get far.

333
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:17,919
Haiyang.

334
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,080
You look around nearby.

335
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,240
Maybe we're overthinking it.

336
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,000
Xiaochuan.

337
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:22,879
Take a few people to the nearby bus station

338
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,720
and the pier to search.

339
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:25,159
Got it, brother.

340
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:25,679
Let's go.

341
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:26,399
Come on.

342
00:12:26,639 --> 00:12:27,559
Come on, get in.

343
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:33,399
I've told you so many times already.

344
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,679
I don't know. I don't know!

345
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,960
Where on earth did you take my child?

346
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:38,399
Give her back to me!

347
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:39,879
All you know how to do is cry all day long.

348
00:12:40,639 --> 00:12:41,039
You...

349
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:42,279
Sis! Sis!

350
00:12:42,519 --> 00:12:43,279
What are you doing?

351
00:12:44,679 --> 00:12:45,600
I already said it.

352
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,240
I said I don't know, so I don't know!

353
00:12:48,759 --> 00:12:50,200
What's wrong with family holding the child?

354
00:12:50,519 --> 00:12:51,720
Would my mom hurt the child?

355
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,840
Give her back!

356
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,000
Bring her back!

357
00:12:54,279 --> 00:12:54,799
You're still crying?

358
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:55,960
Are you mourning the dead?

359
00:12:56,159 --> 00:12:57,320
Bao'er is your daughter too!

360
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:58,519
Now the child is missing.

361
00:12:58,559 --> 00:13:00,639
Do you act like a father at all?

362
00:13:00,759 --> 00:13:01,879
Let's find the child first.

363
00:13:02,159 --> 00:13:02,960
Our family affairs...

364
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,519
...are none of your damn business.

365
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:06,559
Watch your mouth.

366
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:07,600
Fine, Zheng Minjiang.

367
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:08,840
You're amazing.

368
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:09,879
You're tough.

369
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,399
Coming to my house to push me around.

370
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,600
Let me tell you.

371
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,039
This is my house.

372
00:13:15,279 --> 00:13:17,080
No one has the right to lecture me.

373
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,200
Li Guangming!

374
00:13:18,399 --> 00:13:18,720
You...

375
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,440
Yingrong.

376
00:13:19,879 --> 00:13:21,080
Finding the child is what matters now.

377
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:22,279
Sister Yingzhu.

378
00:13:22,679 --> 00:13:23,600
You just wait here at home.

379
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:24,840
Maybe your mother-in-law...

380
00:13:25,039 --> 00:13:26,360
...will bring Bao'er back any time now.

381
00:13:26,879 --> 00:13:27,480
Yingrong and I...

382
00:13:27,799 --> 00:13:28,639
...will go out and look around first.

383
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:30,360
Right, Sis.

384
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:31,919
I will definitely bring Bao'er back.

385
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:34,679
Let's go.

386
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:36,799
Pah!

387
00:13:36,799 --> 00:13:39,159
Where on earth did you hide Bao'er?

388
00:13:39,159 --> 00:13:40,639
It can't really be like my sister said...

389
00:13:40,919 --> 00:13:41,919
...that his mom threw the child away.

390
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,159
We'll find the child.

391
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,159
Don't worry.

392
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:46,559
Let's go.

393
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,440
Hello.

394
00:13:49,559 --> 00:13:50,840
Have you seen an old lady about this tall...

395
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:51,879
...holding a child?

396
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,960
Haven't seen her. Haven't seen her.

397
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:53,600
Hello.

398
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,080
May I ask...

399
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,279
...if you've seen an old lady...

400
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,000
...holding a small child?

401
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,639
About this big.

402
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:57,799
Didn't see her.

403
00:13:58,039 --> 00:13:58,600
You...

404
00:13:58,960 --> 00:13:59,759
You go ask over there.

405
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:00,480
About this big.

406
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,120
Hello, have you seen...

407
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:01,639
...a child about this big?

408
00:14:01,639 --> 00:14:02,200
Did you see them?

409
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:02,840
No, didn't see them.

410
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:03,639
Didn't see them.

411
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:06,480
Watch out!

412
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,759
Watch where you're going!

413
00:14:09,519 --> 00:14:10,039
Are you okay?

414
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,000
I'm fine.

415
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,360
We asked so many people...

416
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:13,799
...and there's no news at all.

417
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,799
Then we keep asking.

418
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,039
We'll definitely find out something.

419
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:16,919
Trust me.

420
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:17,960
Engineer Zheng!

421
00:14:18,399 --> 00:14:19,240
Engineer Zheng!

422
00:14:21,639 --> 00:14:22,679
Any news?

423
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:24,600
I found out.

424
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,960
They're at Furongjiang.

425
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:26,840
Furongjiang?

426
00:14:28,919 --> 00:14:29,320
Zheng!

427
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,679
Chase them on the bike!

428
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:32,039
That woman, Wang Yingzhu...

429
00:14:32,039 --> 00:14:33,000
...is just out of her mind.

430
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:36,240
This child is very healthy.

431
00:14:36,759 --> 00:14:38,679
She's young. You take her home and raise her...

432
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:40,759
...and you'll definitely bond with her.

433
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,919
One thousand yuan. It's a bargain for you.

434
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,120
Is it a girl?

435
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,360
It is a girl.

436
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:47,080
As long as it's a girl.

437
00:14:50,399 --> 00:14:51,440
Let's go, let's go.
